{"tid":2360702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【連溫泉都係假？】7人四川浸溫泉竟離奇觸電 19歲少女傷重昏迷至今 網民：溫泉造假以電加熱","createTime":"2021-01-10T04:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T04:55:42.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"80a3f823e9f137070f26b80af47fdf75b04e67c1","tid":2360702,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:33:44.000Z","msg":"在神州大地上，任何離奇的事件都有可能發生，其中四川早前就發生了多人因浸溫泉而觸電的事件，有內地網民懷疑是浸了用電加熱的「假溫泉」而引起意外。<br />\n內地傳媒報道，事發在上年12月29日，在四川自貢市自流井區的「海湯神泉」溫泉館中，有7名男女在浸溫泉期間突遭電擊，部份人更電至失去意識反起白眼，最後浮在水面，有兩名女傷者情況嚴重，其中1名19歲女子更昏迷至今，當時被送往當地華西醫院，其母更批評溫泉館人員事後叫她直將女兒送到殯儀館。<br />\n有部分在場為傷者急救的救援者就向傳媒表示，當時仍能感到水池中有電流。而涉事的溫泉館現在已停業整頓，但有關當局至今仍未確定事故原因，溫泉館也沒有交代事件。事件引起不少內地網民討論，有人質疑涉事的溫泉造假，是以電加熱的「假溫泉」，所以才漏電引起今次意外，有網民更笑指「哪有甚麼真溫泉」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/happening/713625/【連溫泉都係假？】7人四川浸溫泉竟離奇觸電-19歲少女傷重昏迷至今-網民：溫泉造假以電加熱/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fhappening%2F713625%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%A3%E6%BA%AB%E6%B3%89%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E5%81%87%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%917%E4%BA%BA%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E6%B5%B8%E6%BA%AB%E6%B3%89%E7%AB%9F%E9%9B%A2%E5%A5%87%E8%A7%B8%E9%9B%BB-19%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%82%B7%E9%87%8D%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%9A%E6%BA%AB%E6%B3%89%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87%E4%BB%A5%E9%9B%BB%E5%8A%A0%E7%86%B1%2F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=88d5e418\" target=\"_blank\">https://fortuneinsight.com/web/happening/713625/【連溫泉都係假？】7人四川浸溫泉竟離奇觸電-19歲少女傷重昏迷至今-網民：溫泉造假以電加熱/</a>"},{"pid":"a9466937db3ff89ba04c1a1cb20a375f9cfcfdfa","tid":2360702,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:35:00.000Z","msg":"冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那邊有電用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02909c63ef52c01b22b3d27f19a1933c83d4d60f","tid":2360702,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"，是以電加熱的「假溫泉」，所以才漏電引起今次意外，有網民及連登著名會員吳郭魚更笑指「哪有甚麼真溫泉」。"},{"pid":"79adb5cab8d27660a5bff5161aa8801c09c81b40","tid":2360702,"uid":34409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:51:10.000Z","msg":"部份人更電至失去意識反起白眼，最後浮在水面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADq7zZ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADq7zZ1.jpg&h=05f2473c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43dddae23dd146ad680d00158a50c8ec876f482c","tid":2360702,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79adb5cab8d27660a5bff5161aa8801c09c81b40","tid":2360702,"uid":34409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:51:10.000Z","msg":"部份人更電至失去意識反起白眼，最後浮在水面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADq7zZ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADq7zZ1.jpg&h=05f2473c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62372a2418f096e22ff4341941b230903842fb4a","tid":2360702,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"溫水煮蛙?"},{"pid":"ab57f4570b4b9cce5a2d3d641cbd5926156e3f83","tid":2360702,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"強國堆溫泉<br />\n<br />\n比你浸 都要諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}